About This Company
Caledonian College of Engineering (CCE), one of the premier private colleges in Oman, is once again undergoing a period of expansion with the opening of an additional campus at Airport Heights. Applications are thus invited from qualified, dedicated and experienced personnel for a variety of positions in both academic and administrative departments. CCE provides outstanding opportunities for staff development and qualification enhancement and offers mechanisms to support faculty in undertaking research projects.
